headline: Prologis Stock: Tariff-Concerned Investors Are Overlooking This $42 Billion Growth Driver
summary: Prologis owns industrial properties and warehouses in key transportation hubs around the world.  Investors have been worried about the impact of tariffs on Prologis' business.  The world will likely adjust to tariffs and give Prologis ample opportunity to take advantage of this $42 billion growth driver.
